                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18180909-241-off1323 t18180909-241-cd1324"></join>, two half-crowns and one penny, the monies of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18180909-241-victim1804" type="victimName">
                           John 
